               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The authority has a potential requirement to place a 5 years contract for the repair of fire control equipment fitted to the Challenger 2 vehicle. There will also be the provision for 2 x 1 year options should these be required and subject to satisfactory supplier performance.</P>
